### 6.1 API 側で必要な変更

**オプション A: レスポンスマッピングの追加** (推奨)

`masters.controller.ts` でレスポンスを整形:

```typescript
@Get('subscription-groups')
async listSubscriptionGroups() {
  const result = await this.subscriptionGroupsService.getSubscriptionGroups();

  // Flutter が期待する形式に変換
  const transformedGroups = result.subscriptionGroups.map(group => ({
    id: group.id,
    name: group.teamType === 'single' ? 'Solo Plans' : 'Team Plans',  // 適切な名前を設定
    description: `${group.teamType} subscription plans`,
    plans: group.subscriptions.map(sub => ({
      id: sub.id,
      name: sub.name,
      description: sub.description,
      type: null,  // 必要に応じて設定
      maxBalls: sub.items?.[0]?.balls?.[0]?.availableCount ?? null,
      maxAiCoachs: sub.items?.[0]?.aiCoachs?.[0]?.availableCount ?? null,
      isPaid: sub.isPaid,
